sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Button } from "../ButtonElements"; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, ImgWrap, Column2, Img, } from "./InfoElements"; const InfoSection = ({ lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headline, description, darkText, buttonLabel, img, alt, }) => ( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ); export default InfoSection;
